olor: red;\">莫雷, 電競, 支持911, 呢三件事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n傳開去, 感謝手足!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n    祝<br />\n光復香港, 時代革命"},{"pid":"ac8af0896758b177afc0da928d01d4daf081cc7b","tid":1637981,"uid":114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:14:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38e67881a43e98d8c76fa38068d265ee018ecb5c","tid":1637981,"uid":114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:14:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"acd3aa4a59624ac8e8bc56fc7d02ba4562e37157","tid":1637981,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43177a1525eb2535f8a066204dd321ca5a7499d6","tid":1637981,"uid":114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:14:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0a660695dce81058fcf5b2ed7a800f61b834f12","tid":1637981,"uid":114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:14:53.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"d62856581ebfe266451f7ee8e16b87e4ffba0cc1","tid":1637981,"uid":114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:15:09.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"70b89ae4bec49d879a689eda38dcf3a86c3cde3b","tid":1637981,"uid":114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:15:22.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"e5aa6422f32e21109a060e53e039e24be372ab68","tid":1637981,"uid":114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:15:32.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"373f9670295337f